description: Executes an Analytics query for data

workspace_id.description: ID of the workspace. This is Workspace ID from the Properties blade in the Azure portal.

query.description: The Analytics query. Learn more about the [Analytics query syntax](https://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/articles/app-insights-analytics-reference/)

timespan.description: Optional. The timespan over which to query data. This is an ISO8601 time period value.  This timespan is applied in addition to any that are specified in the query expression.
